Shopping Prices

{{ shipping.type }} {{ shipping.price | currency }}
import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Observable } from "rxjs"; import { CartService } from "../cart.service"; @Component({ selector: 'app-shopping', templateUrl: './shopping.component.html', styleUrls: ['./shopping.component.css'] }) export class ShoppingComponent implements OnInit { constructor(private cartService: CartService) {} shippongCosts!: Observable<{ type: string; price: number }[]>; ngOnInit(): void { this.shippongCosts = this.cartService.getShoppingPrices(); } }
